The route from D to C is one-way only (you can not move from C to D). All compass spins on this stage are random. B to C is 30%, B to E is 70% (according to Japanese wiki [[http://wikiwiki.jp/kancolle/?%C4%C3%BC%E9%C9%DC%B3%A4%B0%E8#area3]]). Keep trying if you're getting detoured to the maelstrom. Do note that F has heavy cruisers and the boss node has a battleship.

